name: Lemon Chilli

reviews.review_text: I had an amazing experience at Lemon Chilli, this is a restaurant where you would go to try every dish listed on the menu. The Quality of ingredients used, cooking techniques, flavours, textures, everything is so very well balanced. The service is great with stewards serving with a smile, and they do their job with passion. I would definitely recommend this restaurant. It's a must try place if you are in Porvorim.

Very good service and fantastic food! Would definitely come again, it's my new favourite! The Paneer Dry Fry was brilliant ;  could not add it to the recommended dishes as it didn't appear as an option, but definitely want to recommend it to veg and non veg people both!

Restaurant Review: Lemon Chilli, Porvorim

Lemon Chilli in Porvorim is a gem that excels in both service and cuisine. From the moment we walked in, the staff impressed us with their warm and humble demeanor, ensuring a seamless dining experience.

We started with the Spicy Kokum Cocktail, a creative and refreshing twist on classic flavors with a perfect balance of tang and spice. The food was equally impressive. The Fried Calamari was crispy, tender, and seasoned to perfection—a great way to kick off our meal. The standout dishes were the Mutton Osso Bucco, which was rich, hearty, and fall-off-the-bone tender, and the Prawn Gnocchi, a unique fusion dish that paired delicate, melt-in-your-mouth gnocchi with succulent prawns in a flavor-packed sauce.

Overall, Lemon Chilli delivers on all fronts: excellent food, impeccable service, and a cozy ambiance. We will definitely be back to explore more of their menu. Highly recommended!

description:
### Welcome to Lemon Chilli: An Exquisite Culinary Escape

Nestled in the heart of Corlim Ind. Estate, **Lemon Chilli** boasts an impressive **rating of 4.8** from an enthusiastic **1,072 reviewers**. This restaurant has quickly become a must-visit destination for food lovers, particularly praised for its standout dishes like **puri**, **churros**, and succulent **pork ribs**. With such diverse foodie tags, it's clear that Lemon Chilli offers something for everyone.

### Ambiance & Design

From the moment you step inside Lemon Chilli, you'll be enveloped in a warm, inviting atmosphere. The décor harmonizes contemporary elegance with local charm, featuring tasteful art pieces and soft lighting that create an intimate and cozy dining experience. Reviewers have noted the restaurant's friendly vibe, amplified by cheerful music that perfectly complements the ambiance. Subtle color palettes and comfortable seating arrangements invite you to relax and appreciate your culinary journey.

![Cozy Dining Experience](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnxAoHfRww9ukPd6_h17uzS9KOOJILqlXgNvln1U50wrqjsMDY2dAX4QeCOX5GROcKF6BGwppQBcax9SBrUpJ23sirilEGYeCs3r8g3pmgGPLwMSTaQ9sqm4IA6Cv5Wk_w3skbjKw=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The culinary offerings at Lemon Chilli are nothing short of spectacular. Known for its meticulous attention to flavor and texture, the menu is a delightful journey through various cuisines. Notably, the **Spicy Kokum Cocktail** and **Fried Calamari** have emerged as crowd favorites, each embodying a blend of innovative flair and traditional essence. The **Mutton Osso Bucco** shines as a signature dish, delivering a rich and hearty experience, while the **Prawn Gnocchi** is a unique fusion that pairs delicate pasta with succulent prawns, aptly receiving rave reviews for its deliciousness.

Additionally, for those who are health-conscious or have dietary preferences, Lemon Chilli accommodates various needs, making it a versatile dining option.

![Mouthwatering Dishes](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdm0r4bkqO239EZtd9twJSXbhBe7Fkas6vO8J_46D4s7d2KXXY_2nVJDO5NNmgq-zstn1qNgQGJsCd-b0Pg5yvtLu6NF8Kha21AAp4cr393JMywOK9klBepPQP75sWF9Lc0gFvKU=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Lemon Chilli's service is consistently highlighted across reviews—guests commend the staff for their professionalism and warmth. Attentive and engaging, servers greet diners with genuine smiles and ensure a flawless service experience. Many patrons express a strong desire to return, citing the passion with which staff approach their roles. Reservations are encouraged, especially during peak dining hours, ensuring you have a spot at this beloved eatery.

### Popularity & Reviews

The buzz surrounding Lemon Chilli is palpable, with many diners proclaiming it as their **new favorite** spot. Social media is abuzz with photos of vibrant dishes and satisfied customers, helping amplify its reputation further. Critics and food enthusiasts alike have lauded its innovative cooking and community-centered approach, marking it as a standout in the local dining scene.

![Customer Delight](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmtuaa5ydc7iR9kUGhlJtrURIoaru7hdkm2PNaqg9umkto90QC2JwqPVDCoc-xSB8oP1Zk2kaeP2bV6umcekikkQUslRtXzxjDTz43S66beUBjHzOBFuP_bhn_HnbufzvWs9zeq=w375-h281-p)

### Concluding Reflections

In summary, Lemon Chilli is not just a restaurant; it’s a culinary adventure that celebrates the joy of eating. With its exquisite menu, cozy atmosphere, and excellent service, it’s no wonder that this eatery stands out in the vibrant landscape of Corlim Ind. Estate. Whether you’re indulging in their **churros**, **pork ribs**, or simply savoring a refreshing cocktail, your experience here is sure to be unforgettable. If you're in the area, make Lemon Chilli a priority on your dining list - a delightful experience awaits! 

![Dining Experience at Lemon Chilli](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlHi5-AqGVL8zFMAINBWD2EhdKuy-I8iMvtTUfSugfVNVg8abw6L3T4KQggfjHDKD2YA8Zz2hrL9iClXh0PgPvHxAr4OyqxNCCSYjIq9V6FrdTjSpT-X6QX8bGOi3ahYrj8JjqF=w375-h281-p)
